var isProduction = "production" === 'production';
function warning(condition, message) {
  if (!isProduction) {
    if (condition) {
      return;
    }

    var text = "Warning: " + message;

    if (typeof console !== 'undefined') {
      console.warn(text);
    }

    try {
      throw Error(text);
    } catch (x) {}
  }
}
